dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Shawano County, WI 2016
dc_description_s: These data layers represent roads and right of ways (ROW) for Shawano County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Shawano_Roads_ROW_2016.gdb'. [Roads: Shawano County Wisconsin County-wide transportation centerline layer. ROW: Right of Way polygons.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
